{"id": "ChIJ2c7yiPGBhYARYJisAG2zKpk", "rating": 4.4, "userRatingCount": 23, "displayName": {"text": "Yoeechee", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ2c7yiPGBhYARYJisAG2zKpk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kV1owNWFXRmxRT1dWR1lsWTJkMFp6TWpacFJIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I visited during dinner time, and everything was incredibly fresh with no fishy taste at all.\n\nThe eel rice bowl was delicious, the eel had a nice chewy texture and was perfectly seasoned. The 6-piece nigiri sushi set was exactly what you’d hope for: fresh, high-quality fish with great balance and flavor.\n\nThe salmon don was served with half fresh salmon sashimi and half grilled salmon, which made for a nice variety of flavors and textures. It was especially good when wrapped in the seaweed provided.\n\nThe atmosphere felt like a premium sushi takeout spot, clean, modern, and upscale. Even during the dinner rush, all of the seafood tasted very fresh.\n\nUnfortunately, they were sold out of uni when I visited😢 so I’ll definitely be coming back to try it next time. They seem to offer a wide variety of sushi options, and if you’re looking for the best selection, I’d recommend visiting during lunch hours!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I visited during dinner time, and everything was incredibly fresh with no fishy taste at all.\n\nThe eel rice bowl was delicious, the eel had a nice chewy texture and was perfectly seasoned. The 6-piece nigiri sushi set was exactly what you’d hope for: fresh, high-quality fish with great balance and flavor.\n\nThe salmon don was served with half fresh salmon sashimi and half grilled salmon, which made for a nice variety of flavors and textures. It was especially good when wrapped in the seaweed provided.\n\nThe atmosphere felt like a premium sushi takeout spot, clean, modern, and upscale. Even during the dinner rush, all of the seafood tasted very fresh.\n\nUnfortunately, they were sold out of uni when I visited😢 so I’ll definitely be coming back to try it next time. They seem to offer a wide variety of sushi options, and if you’re looking for the best selection, I’d recommend visiting during lunch hours!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jane Jung", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108635421073540465732/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKSUgsNKXwmF6vak2DR1oML6euflmSW-r4niIZZVBq9l-jlcR0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-17T03:45:45.686702022Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kV1owNWFXRmxRT1dWR1lsWTJkMFp6TWpacFJIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kV1owNWFXRmxRT1dWR1lsWTJkMFp6TWpacFJIYxAB!2m1!1s0x808581f188f2ced9:0x992ab36d00ac9860"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2c7yiPGBhYARYJisAG2zKpk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kdU4wTk5NakJwV1VoSE0ydFRSV3RxYmw5eGNVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The fish was incredibly fresh, and the portions were very generous, which is rare to find these days. Everything was absolutely delicious - the fish was tender and literally melted in my mouth. I loved the variety in the set and the beautiful presentation. You can really tell they use high-quality ingredients and don’t cut corners on portion sizes. I will definitely order again and highly recommend it to anyone who loves great sushi and sashimi 🍣", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The fish was incredibly fresh, and the portions were very generous, which is rare to find these days. Everything was absolutely delicious - the fish was tender and literally melted in my mouth. I loved the variety in the set and the beautiful presentation. You can really tell they use high-quality ingredients and don’t cut corners on portion sizes. I will definitely order again and highly recommend it to anyone who loves great sushi and sashimi 🍣", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Volha Creative", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104982474406990667807/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZqf05JCKX6C8dirTMkd1z8bOHHKjX4T4e0zdNB1HwRYb7jio=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-06T20:06:59.736875191Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kdU4wTk5NakJwV1VoSE0ydFRSV3RxYmw5eGNVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kdU4wTk5NakJwV1VoSE0ydFRSV3RxYmw5eGNVRRAB!2m1!1s0x808581f188f2ced9:0x992ab36d00ac9860"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2c7yiPGBhYARYJisAG2zKpk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psVGVXYzVibE5mTWtaWU9WOXpSMlJ3TmxGTFRtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I popped in to grab a quick lunch and I’m so glad I did! All the boxes were so beautiful and the gentleman helping me was very helpful. I chose the six-piece box and it tasted as good as it looked. Amazing quality!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I popped in to grab a quick lunch and I’m so glad I did! All the boxes were so beautiful and the gentleman helping me was very helpful. I chose the six-piece box and it tasted as good as it looked. Amazing quality!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Melissa Canfield", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103841012716288422292/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIeiR3wMcfqTXMRmTsxPMUIg3MgZjEt287mQd3dgI7fuE0S=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-27T01:13:18.486749850Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psVGVXYzVibE5mTWtaWU9WOXpSMlJ3TmxGTFRtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psVGVXYzVibE5mTWtaWU9WOXpSMlJ3TmxGTFRtYxAB!2m1!1s0x808581f188f2ced9:0x992ab36d00ac9860"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2c7yiPGBhYARYJisAG2zKpk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xScFMycEVWM2RKYlVoTWRUSnpVVGc1WTBRMVZrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Brand new omakase takeout sushi.\n\nReally exceptional quality, the boxes are pricey (low $20 to ~$50) but absolutely worth it.\n\nWas skeptical because of the vibe the glass case gave off but was really delicious.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Brand new omakase takeout sushi.\n\nReally exceptional quality, the boxes are pricey (low $20 to ~$50) but absolutely worth it.\n\nWas skeptical because of the vibe the glass case gave off but was really delicious.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Nathan Garvie", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111388345718630350923/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwvvg8pHBVHUiIf9qj-UXAMbcsW2oTlyYG6R0LzZ79Q58Z0xzx=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-22T19:12:48.677716390Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xScFMycEVWM2RKYlVoTWRUSnpVVGc1WTBRMVZrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xScFMycEVWM2RKYlVoTWRUSnpVVGc1WTBRMVZrRRAB!2m1!1s0x808581f188f2ced9:0x992ab36d00ac9860"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2c7yiPGBhYARYJisAG2zKpk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoV1EzRXdRbVZuWm5oTlRrb3RVRTlWYkhsVlUzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "The service was good. However, the food itself didn’t feel worth the price. The amount of fish looked noticeably smaller than in the photos, and the shari was disappointing. The nigiri also didn’t feel very well-shaped or carefully made. The wasabi had no real flavor or heat.\n\nOne thing I didn’t really understand was the recommendation to let it sit out for 30–45 minutes before eating. That didn’t feel ideal for sushi, especially with raw seafood, and it made the food feel less fresh.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The service was good. However, the food itself didn’t feel worth the price. The amount of fish looked noticeably smaller than in the photos, and the shari was disappointing. The nigiri also didn’t feel very well-shaped or carefully made. The wasabi had no real flavor or heat.\n\nOne thing I didn’t really understand was the recommendation to let it sit out for 30–45 minutes before eating. That didn’t feel ideal for sushi, especially with raw seafood, and it made the food feel less fresh.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Liam Ayase", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106061461813663776226/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSfjXxjiWgz2SLMXQcEyGnDTnpDyN2ekaVK0MOkTeQEUq5yAe2=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-11T09:56:59.320556604Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoV1EzRXdRbVZuWm5oTlRrb3RVRTlWYkhsVlUzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoV1EzRXdRbVZuWm5oTlRrb3RVRTlWYkhsVlUzYxAB!2m1!1s0x808581f188f2ced9:0x992ab36d00ac9860"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ2c7yiPGBhYARYJisAG2zKpk/photos/AWCwydgYQNbMZPcWHxP9InEhQ64qze8LaznBRVxy-sYNZFwIPaP5ai7o_C_FDghGVC3hIVZblP_ELSN8mcW26wXt5sMwL3N2yT2OeUDrt_CsruePwQNAldRGmPEqStg4snv8yBnDtauXQvFOSi8rApRpd1WIV8_mhgOv9OoIZP0-5X-CcooyMDlqybyH0xadESfNhebduZfpl7-8HBHg-c8mo_yyU0kGgX0C_U3PQxRS5lfzf5bPQbPcwDgmdGfMt19VsGDhrNOhVlpv0uwfWC3q10GKjzme0hc_xFSYqEF_kUgO-fcJANxuZy3T_lctMdl2utI2dZETziiYq6qvbw0gNoKT-58hNe43sEPEDt3a8T8vapAbAqVBwi1WgNwGK3LvoaVjilL6-fdlYs52_jsLzyncSRhBo8fp8PLP4CtctmDZIuS16WM6_zYhtgfxig", "wi